<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shark/Ninja Robot Vacuum - Annie Sommer</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
   <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,opsz,wght@0,14..32,100..900;1,14..32,100..900&family=Newsreader:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..72,200..800;1,6..72,200..800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
        :root {
   			 --primary-color: #334EAC; /* Royal */
   			 --secondary-color: #081F5C; /* Midnight */
   			 --accent-color: #7096D1; /* China */
  			--text-color: #334EAC; /* Royal for main text */
  			--text-secondary: #7096D1; /* China for secondary text */
   			 --text-muted: #BAD6EB; /* Sky for muted text */
   			 --light-gray: #F7F2EB; /* Moon */
   			 --border-color: #EDF1F6; /* Porcelain */
   			 --background-accent: #D0E3FF; /* Dawn */
            --sidebar-width: 240px; 
            --base-font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: var(--base-font-size);
        }
        
        .container {
            display: flex;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            gap: 3rem;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        
        /* Sidebar */
        .sidebar {
            width: var(--sidebar-width);
            flex-shrink: 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 2rem;
            height: fit-content;
        }
        
        .back-link {
            color: #7096D1
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            display: block;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .back-link:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        
        
        .toc {
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .toc h3 {
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .toc ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .toc li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .toc a {
            color: var(--text-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            padding: 0.25rem 0;
            display: block;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .toc a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            background-color: rgba(247, 242, 235, 0.25);
            padding-left: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* Active TOC link styling */
        .toc a.active {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            background-color:	rgba(247, 242, 235, 0.45);
            padding-left: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
        }
        /* Smooth transition for TOC links */
        .toc a {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-left: 3px solid transparent;
        }
        
        /* Main Content */
        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0;
            max-width: 760px;
        }
        
        .project-header {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .project-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .project-meta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #7096D1;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .project-summary {
            font-size: .9rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .content-section {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .content-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        
        .content-section h3 {
            font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        
        .content-section p {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: var(--base-font-size);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .content-section ul, .content-section ol {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: var(--base-font-size);
            margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
        }
        
        .content-section li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .highlight-box {
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .highlight-box h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        
        .highlight-box p, .highlight-box ul {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: var(--base-font-size);
        }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            display: block;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #7096D1;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .image-placeholder {
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #7096D1;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Thumbnail styling */
        .thumbnail {
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .thumbnail:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .thumbnail img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .thumbnail:hover img {
            filter: brightness(1.1);
        }

        /* Fullscreen modal */
        .modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 1000;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
        }

        .modal.active {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .modal-content {
            max-width: 90vw;
            max-height: 80vh;
            object-fit: contain;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .modal-caption {
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        .modal-close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 2rem;
            right: 2rem;
            color: white;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
        }

        .modal-close:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
        
        .navigation {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 4rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        
        .nav-link {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .nav-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Mobile Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 1rem;
                gap: 2rem;
            }
            
            .sidebar {
                width: 100%;
                position: static;
                order: 2;
            }
            
            .main-content {
                order: 1;
            }
            
            .project-header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .project-meta {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.5rem;
            }

            /* Mobile responsive for modal */
            .modal-content {
                max-width: 95vw;
                max-height: 70vh;
            }
            
            .modal-close {
                top: 1rem;
                right: 1rem;
                width: 35px;
                height: 35px;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .modal-caption {
                font-size: 1rem;
                margin-top: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Sidebar with TOC -->
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <a href="/" class="back-link">← home </a>
            <nav class="toc">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#problem">User Problem</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#strategy">Strategy</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#process">Process</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#solution">Solution</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#design">Design Details</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#insights">Insights</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </aside>
        
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <main class="main-content">
            <header class="project-header">
                <h1>Prolitec Aera</h1>
                
                <div class="project-meta">
                    <span><strong>Role:</strong> Lead Product Designer</span>
                    <span><strong>Client:</strong> Prolitec</span>
                    <span><strong>Platform:</strong> Alexa & Google Home Skills</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="project-summary">
                    Voice and mobile UX/UI design for a connected home-scenting system. Prolitec’s first consumer product. 
                </div>
            </header>
            
            <section class="content-section" id="problem">
                <h2>User Problem</h2>
                <p>Users needed a convenient way to control their electric scent diffuser without getting up.</p>
                <h2>Business Problem</h2>
                <p>Prolitec was launching its first consumer-facing IoT product and needed a voice and app interface that conveyed reliability, elegance, and technical confidence.</p>
                 <div class="image-placeholder">
                    <div class="thumbnail" data-caption="User testing revealed that people form emotional connections with their robot vacuums, treating them like pets with names and personalities.">
                        <img src="/img/Prolitec/pinkdiffuser1.png" alt="The Aera device was tech-forward but brand photography was editorial, which we took early inspiration from ">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="content-section" id="strategy">
                <h2>Strategy</h2>
                
                <h3>My Role</h3>
                <p>I was the lead product designer on the Alexa and Google Home skills, and worked with a fellow designer who was tackling the mobile use case.</p>
                
                <p>I brought the more ephemeral elements of home scenting as well as the high-end, tech forward legacy of Prolitec through in the VUI.</p>
                
                <h3>Approach</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Research:</strong> Copy and brand research went into how people think about scents and what they would actually say to Alexa about their diffuser</li>
                    <li><strong>Refine requirements:</strong> Typical iOT features like settings and schedules were earmarked by engineering. Our iOT solution required naming, which was cumbersome.</li>
                    <li><strong>Design:</strong> I designed the VUI including the VUI diagram, copy and tone writing, introduction text, and worked with mobile teams to sync with the mobile app</li>
                    <li><strong>Ship:</strong> I and another designer worked to synchronize the iOS and Android apps with the voice skill and the copy and shipped them at the same time</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            
            <section class="content-section" id="solution">
                <h2>Solution</h2>
                <p>The company was tech-forward vs. scent-forward.</p>
                
                <p>We repositioned the brand tone from purely technical to sensory-forward, using scent moods and sound design to elevate the emotional layer of the experience.</p>
                
                <p>The iOT solution requiring naming was solutioned with a "set default device" flow. This allowed users to control the intensity or power on/off without specifying a name for the device, but it required a cumbersome invocation and workflow. </p>
                
                <p>We harmonized the copy on device, in the app, and in the voice skill.  Scent-inspired colors and patterns personalized the UI and were driven home in the VUI through tone and sound effects.</p>
                
                <div class="image-placeholder">
                    <div class="thumbnail" data-caption="User testing revealed that people form emotional connections with their robot vacuums, treating them like pets with names and personalities.">
                        <img src="/img/Prolitec/appUI1.png" alt="The device had a large dial, and we echoed the design of the device inside the mobile app">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="content-section" id="design">
                <h2>Design Details</h2>
                <p>"Alexa, ask Aera to adjust intensity" was awkward, but it's where we started with engineering for the scent intensity feature.</p>
                
                <p>Complexity comes in when you have multiple diffusers.</p>
                
                <p>"Alexa, ask Aera 1 to turn it down" is much more natural but took some finessing and collaboration with copy and engineering to get right.</p>
                
                <p>Determining what "down" meant — 1, 2 scent notches — was also a collaboration with business and had to be determined across the app & voice skill.</p>
                
                <h3>VUI Design Considerations</h3>
                <p>A huge UX barrier on VUIs was the constant need to define devices using names. Users would receive an inquiry as to the name of their device in most cases based on hardware limitations.</p>
                
                <p>We navigated this by keeping Alexa's queries short and to the point, and offering strategic paths and queries to different functionalities in the VUI such as the "set default device" flow</p>
                
                <div class="image-placeholder">
                    <div class="thumbnail" data-caption="User testing revealed that people form emotional connections with their robot vacuums, treating them like pets with names and personalities.">
                        <img src="/img/Prolitec/prolitecVUIdiagram.jpg" alt="VUI diagram showing the complexity of seemingly simple voice user interface workflows">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
            </section>
            <section class="content-section" id="insights">
                <h2>Insights</h2>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Setting a Mood</h3>
                    <p>Enabling the brand to communicate competence and credibility came first before any ephemeral features as IoT users are often frustrated. I drove this throughout the design process.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Engineering Partnership is Key</h3>
                    <p>Working with engineering to co-create feasible fallback interaction paths for unsupported utterances like naming your scent diffuser is crucial to avoid awkwardness in voice interfaces and prevent user discomfort in their homes.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
            
